title: TCDD MT5400
text: TCDD MT5400 is a series of 20 diesel <a href="railcar">railcar</a>s operated by the <a href="Turkish%20State%20Railways">Turkish State Railways</a>. They were produced by <a href="Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9%20Centrale%20de%20Chemins%20de%20Fer">Société Centrale de Chemins de Fer</a> of France in 1954–55. Also delivered were 30 trailers numbered MR401 through MR430.
